#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int t;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--)
    {
        int n,l;
        set<int>s;
        cin>>n;
        for(int i=0;i<n;i++)
        {
            cin>>l;
            s.insert(l);
        }
        if(s.size()==n)
        cout<<"YES"<<endl;

        else
            cout<<"NO"<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
